cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this data, methodology, or code in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "Open Spatial Analysis of Agricultural Burning Patterns in Northern Thailand"
abstract: >
  Satellite-derived burn forensics for Chiang Mai province, 2018–2026.
  Uses NASA FIRMS active fire detections and Copernicus Sentinel-2 dNBR to map
  burn recurrence, spatial clustering, and temporal coordination of fire events
  across northern Thailand.
authors:
  - name: "ChiangFai Open Research"
    alias: "ChiangFai"
repository-code: "https://github.com/ChiangFai/ChiangFai"
url: "https://github.com/ChiangFai/ChiangFai"
license: MIT
date-released: "2026-03-29"
version: "1.0.0"
keywords:
  - wildfire
  - remote sensing
  - Google Earth Engine
  - NASA FIRMS
  - Sentinel-2
  - Thailand
  - Chiang Mai
  - dNBR
  - burn mapping
  - agricultural burning
  - spatial analysis
  - open data
references:
